channel.description: Hi guys i need help to change the starter place, and im using richscape source.

item.title: Need help with..., -read more-
item.dc:creator: @runefreak10 runefreak10
item.description:
@runefreak10 wrote:

Go into Player.java and search for: teleportToX =

Keep searching through until you see something like this:

teleportToX = 2848; // 2848; teleportToY = 9636; // 9636;

That is my starting position but look for that setup and then just change the coords to whatever you want.
